Third Department,

February, 1983

(February 1, 1983) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Robert Nash, Petitioner, v Eugene S. LeFevre, as Superintendent of Clinton Correctional Facility, Respondent.

— Application, pursuant to CPLR 7002 (subd [b], par 2), for writ *620of habeas corpus denied, upon the ground that it appears from the papers that petitioner is not illegally detained (CPLR 7003, subd [a]). Mahoney, P. J., Sweeney, Kane, Weiss and Levine, JJ., concur.
